lead_paragraph: The Panthers not only disappointed folks in the Carolinas with their Super Bowl performance in February, they also let down Pro Picks. With a chance for a winning record for the 2015 season, we went with Cam Newton and Co. over the Broncos. So we got run over by Von Miller, too.

headline.print_headline: Super Bowl Rematch, Different Outcome for Panthers, Broncos
